    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "interesting. why do you say Candidate B's style borders on unprofessional? i mean, the actual substance of what they said is pretty much identical to Candidate A. is it just the wording, or do u feel like the way they talk might impact how clients perceive their intelligence or competence?",
